{"uid":"65125095a6287af2","name":"test_trap_cleans_up_snapshot_on_exit","fullName":"tests.tasks.test_tasks_ssh_utils.TestRemoteSnapshotCmd#test_trap_cleans_up_snapshot_on_exit","historyId":"c0c3f6f3e1eb52939a9cef6a6d4cf8e7","time":{"start":1780253519451,"stop":1780253519451,"duration":0},"description":"A failing report (or ``Ctrl-C``) must not leak a\nmulti-hundred-MB ``.db`` snapshot in ``/tmp``. The trap is\nregistered before the ``.backup`` so even an interrupt\nbetween registration and completion cannot orphan the file.\n\n``sqlite3 .backup`` writes a single self-contained DB file —\nthere are no ``-wal`` / ``-shm`` sidecars attached to the\nsnapshot output, so the trap does not need to mention them.\n","descriptionHtml":"<p>A failing report (or <code>Ctrl-C</code>) must not leak a<br />\nmulti-hundred-MB <code>.db</code> snapshot in <code>/tmp</code>. The trap is<br />\nregistered before the <code>.backup</code> so even an interrupt<br />\nbetween registration and completion cannot orphan the file.</p>\n<p><code>sqlite3 .backup</code> writes a single self-contained DB file —<br />\nthere are no <code>-wal</code> / <code>-shm</code> sidecars attached to the<br />\nsnapshot output, so the trap does not need to mention them.</p>\n","status":"passed","flaky":false,"newFailed":false,"newBroken":false,"newPassed":false,"retriesCount":0,"retriesStatusChange":false,"beforeStages":[{"name":"_stub_socket_getfqdn","time":{"start":1780253486677,"stop":1780253486678,"duration":1},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"attachmentsCount":0,"stepsCount":0,"hasContent":false,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"monkeypatch","time":{"start":1780253519449,"stop":1780253519449,"duration":0},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"attachmentsCount":0,"stepsCount":0,"hasContent":false,"attachmentStep":false},{"name":"_reset_db_connection","time":{"start":1780253519450,"stop":17802535